node.text:
At the end of the day, the process is the journey for me. It's the adventure in itself. I got a chance to head back to my home state of Texas to see how @ToyotaUSA builds each Tundra from start to finish. Right in the heart of San Antonio is where we started, and then hit the road to test out the new Tundra TRD as we made our way to Big Bend National Park. What a time we had. Hope you guys enjoy! #Tundra #LetsGoPlaces 

🎥 @tczech
Editor: @rodophoto 
@inkwell.media

node.text:
At the end of the day, the process is the journey for me. It's the adventure in itself. I got a chance to head back to my home state of Texas to see how @ToyotaUSA builds each Tundra from start to finish. Right in the heart of San Antonio is where we started, and then hit the road to test out the new Tundra TRD as we made our way to Big Bend National Park. What a time we had. Hope you guys enjoy! #Tundra #LetsGoPlaces 

🎥 @tczech

node.text: The Maker Unveil Event was one for the books. Being able to witness history in the making is a feeling like no other. Throughout the entire event, all I could think of was that THIS is the future. I got to see this legendary all-electric, vertical takeoff and landing aircraft before it was revealed to the public and it blew my mind. Crazy to think how far technology has come and this is just the beginning. Stoked to be a part of this movement and what's to come. Go follow @flyarcher to come on this adventure with us! Let's get it! 🤘🏻#ArcherInfluencer
